A
40-year-old woman was killed, and three others were severely injured. This after the
speeding Polo GTI driver lost control at a curve and the GTI fell off the newly
built brigde. The
incident occurred at the flyover in the IT corridor of Hyderabad in India on
Saturday afternoon. The Polo
GTI was reportedly over-speeding at 104 kM in a 40 KM zone.  